{"type": "article", "id": 23569, "title": "如果你喜欢中指猫的魔性调调，来看看他们的快闪店", "description": "一个充满戏谑和「微笑」的地方", "date": "2016-03-09T17:59:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7721, "name": "滑板"}, {"id": 24649, "name": "中指猫"}, {"id": 2276, "name": "外星人"}, {"id": 4780, "name": "快闪店"}, {"id": 19764, "name": "街头品牌"}, {"id": 11354, "name": "艺术展览"}, {"id": 17670, "name": "Ripndip"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 157, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702114154nmotVUEO2ae1SxMk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">光是说 Ripndip 这个品牌，不一定有很多人记得，但他们家服装、滑板、袜子、手机壳等等产品上印着的，表情略贱、竖着中指的猫  Lord Nermal 和绿色大脑袋的外星人形象还是挺深入人心的。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114146TlXk580PALspuSE3.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57452575\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114147yrmNYQSzRA3XH5nU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00164204\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">此前我们在<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/13811.html\">报道上海一家街头品牌集合店“ALL SH”</a> 时，曾对 Ripndip 进行过介绍，这样扒开口袋才看得到“ Lord Nermal 猫”不屑问候的 T 恤是店内的畅销品之一。而这一品牌是 2009 年由滑板狂热选手 Ryan O'Connor 在洛杉矶创立，和很多滑板服饰品牌类似，以生产简约的 T 恤、卫衣、棒球帽等为主，最具特色的便是上文提到的那两只充满戏谑神情的吉祥物。这样不羁又带点幽默的感觉，让品牌很快走红，一时间登上很多人的“必 buy 清单”。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114147ck3fU4FwDyG5WOme.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.33518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">而最近，Ripndip 在洛杉矶 Fairfax 大街知名的<a href=\"http://knowngallery.com/blog/post/ripndip-pop-up-shop-and-gallery/\"> Known  Gallery 画廊开了快闪店</a>，庆祝其 2016 系列的发布。内部设有一些神经兮兮、挺诙谐的装置展览，和最新的款式。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114148Z56RPMcNSUpTsFdo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">异想天开的世界里，无处不在的中指猫和外星人：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114148mKLsei0yowCYbFZ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114149JXyT4Gd3MEUPK5ui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114149FutkHJUl087IPXvi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021141507NMZsAEDwrLibcpY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021141509LhycnQ0R7l3IpVm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>中指猫还成为了达利、罗丹和米开朗琪罗等经典作品中的主角。（别笑！）</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114151nz8t9u0IbCjUeVXL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114151IVih6b8S4LtzH5MZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">当然还有丰富的可选单品：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114152OGRDu6pUSWw58HLV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114152eZ9YVhBq5CMFRvrn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">活动一直持续到 3 月 21 日，有机会在洛杉矶的朋友们别错过。</p>\n<p class=\"\">Have fun!</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114153sh7GnVw2giK9luL8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021141532IkcdRnyq8MUYC47.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702114154ZnpHNYObXJQPUwLo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n\n\n"}